{"tw": {"2485860": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "WANDERER: Broken Bed", "steam_appid": 2485860, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [2814150, 2814140, 2814130], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/0e26e143aa46683671e2a08a6cf7f00a.poster.avif?t=1771400736\" width=608 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/0e26e143aa46683671e2a08a6cf7f00a.webm?t=1771400736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《異世界浪子：床榻春宮》是一款帶有約會模擬、指向點擊和角色扮演元素的紳士冒險遊戲，將帶你進入一個充滿歡愉的世界。我們的英雄只是一個普通人，平日只喜歡玩遊戲和看動漫，過着碌碌無為的日子。等到發現自己被傳送到充滿魔法和巫術的異世界，他的生活迎來了翻天覆地的變化。如今，作為天選之人的他想要成為世界的霸主，征服坎寧安魔法學院所有淫婦的小穴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/daf712b9a76315141d4d0ad7a914a098.poster.avif?t=1771400736\" width=300 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/daf712b9a76315141d4d0ad7a914a098.webm?t=1771400736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/468c0d5f2f982cf1b12be4ff4f5e0c1e.poster.avif?t=1771400736\" width=300 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/468c0d5f2f982cf1b12be4ff4f5e0c1e.webm?t=1771400736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;這所享有盛名的學院是由兩位偉大的魔法師於本世紀