dventure game with dating-sim, point-and-click and RPG elements that will take you to a world of pleasures. Our hero is just an ordinary guy, wasting an ordinary life on playing games and watching anime. His life starts to change the moment he finds himself transported to an another world, full of magic and wizardry. Now chosen by fate, he is in a hurry to conquer this new world and the pussies of all lewd girls in the Cunningham Academy of Magical Arts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/daf712b9a76315141d4d0ad7a914a098.poster.avif?t=1771400736\" width=300 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/daf712b9a76315141d4d0ad7a914a098.webm?t=1771400736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/468c0d5f2f982cf1b12be4ff4f5e0c1e.poster.avif?t=1771400736\" width=300 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/468c0d5f2f982cf1b12be4ff4f5e0c1e.webm?t=1771400736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This prestigious academy was founded at the beginning of the century by two great magicians, and accepts only those of noble birth. Here, our hero begins his great journey.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Cunningham Academy of Magical Arts contains much history and secrets, and will become the background to stories that will make your blood run cold. You are going on an exciting journey in an extraordinary world! On the way to the top, you will meet many characters who have their own secrets and mental anguish. You will have to establish relationships with girls, and perhaps, even find true love! And maybe collect a harem...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/b57fb5012d80a43f029727c6cecd62a6.poster.avif?t=1771400736\" width=618 height=311 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/b57fb5012d80a43f029727c6cecd62a6.webm?t=1771400736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇</strong> Interactive and animated sex scenes;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇</strong> Many beautiful erotic cards in the gallery;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇</strong> Root system with many girls and a lot of additional characters;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇</strong> A lot of non-linear quests;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇</strong> Lots of locations and a grand animated world;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇</strong> Enchanting soundtrack; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇</strong> Card battles in the dungeons and the skill system;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇</strong> Puzzles and mini-games;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇</strong> Inventory and interactive objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485860/extras/0e26e143aa46683671e2a08a6cf7f00a.poster.avif?t=1771400736\" width=608 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/